  "_comment": "Phase 3b DRAFT — city-specific Ausländerbehörde sources, ALL-GERMAN. Voyage voyage-3 is multilingual and Claude reads German natively, so we ingest the authoritative German pages and let Claude translate in the answer. NOT yet merged into sources.json. Review, then copy the `sources` entries into sources.json and re-run ingestion.",
  "_policy": {
    "language": "100% German official pages. The German pages are the authoritative version of every German bureaucratic process — English translations on city sites are typically partial summaries. Voyage voyage-3 embeds German + English queries into the same vector space, so an English user query still retrieves the right German chunk; Claude then translates the answer.",
    "rejected_sources": "Third-party aggregators like integreat.app, expats.de, auslaenderaemter.com, and auslaenderbehoerde.org are NOT included — only official city/Bundesland domains.",
    "scope_rationale": "Top 12 cities by non-EU immigrant population. Berlin already covered by service.berlin.de entries in the main sources.json, so it's omitted here.",
    "verified_at": "2026-04-16 — all URLs returned HTTP 200 via curl with Mozilla UA.",
    "cost_estimate": "35 URLs × avg ~5 chunks/URL ≈ ~175 chunks. On Voyage free tier (22s/chunk): ~64 min. On paid tier: ~45s.",
    "ingestion_command": "docker compose exec api-python python scripts/ingest_knowledge.py --only \"stadt.muenchen.de,hamburg.de/auslaenderbehoerde,hamburg.de/politik-und-verwaltung,hamburg.de/service/info/111207615,hamburg.de/service/suche/aufenthaltstitel,amka.de,stadt-koeln.de,stuttgart.de/buergerinnen-und-buerger/migranten,duesseldorf.de/auslaenderamt,duesseldorf.de/amt-fuer-migration,leipzig.de/jugend-familie-und-soziales,dortmund.de/themen/aufenthalt,service.bremen.de/dienstleistungen/aufenthaltserlaubnis-beantragen-nach,service.bremen.de/dienstleistungen/aufenthaltserlaubnis-fuer-eine-erwerb,service.bremen.de/dienstleistungen/elektronischer-aufenthaltstitel,service.niedersachsen.de/detail,nuernberg.de/internet/auslaenderbehoerde\""
